Quiet Operation Our fan utilizes advanced noise control technology, ensuring quiet operation while delivering excellent cooling performance. This means you can enjoy high performance without being disturbed by noisy sounds.

Fan Type Description We have designed two types of products,out and into.Out means out air,the hot air inside the case is pumped out of the case, generally recommended to install on the top of the case and the back of the case, into means into the air, the cold air is pumped into the case, so that the temperature inside the case can be quickly dropped down, generally recommended to install at the bottom of the case,the front of the case, or the side of the case. Of course, if the out and into two types of fans are installed in reverse, it does not affect the use, but the led lighting effect will be poor, according to our suggestions to buy and install the fan, you can make the lighting effect to achieve the best state.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fan to cool your PC and looks cool with RGB lights
reviews.reviewText: I got this mostly for the functionality of cooling my PC and it gets the job done well. Easily connects to my motherboard and was able to get the RGB lights to light up. It doesn't make much noise, at least that I can notice. Though fan noise has never really bothered me. There's not much to say about it. It's a fan for your desktop PC and it looks pretty when it lights up.Next time I need to get a case fan I'll probably get another of these, or one from the same company since I know that it works well.
